overview.en: CNT is a stable, transparent, and secure digital asset issued globally based on CNH. As a stable currency system relying on Ethereum, CNT can be compatible with all ETH wallets, supported by sufficient cash assets to help people integrate into the digital world quickly and conveniently.
overview.zh: CNT是基于离岸人民币，面向全球发行的稳定、透明、安全的数字资产。CNT作为依托以太坊的稳定币系统，能兼容所有的ETH钱包，通过足额的现金类资产为支撑，帮助人们快速、便捷的融入数字世界。
